text: Samsung Galaxy A03 was released in late 2021. It has a display that has a resolution of 1600 x 720 pixels. It has a 48 MP main and 2 MP depth cameras. It has an 8-core processor running at 1.6 GHz with 3 or 4 GB of RAM and 32-128 GB of storage. It supports Wi-Fi 5 (802.11ac) and Bluetooth 5.0.
